Node & Pod Mapping**:\n   - `aiops-k8s-08` hosts important services including `checkoutservice-1`, `cartservice-2`, and `redis-cart-0`, corroborating the impact of node memory issue on service performance.\n\n### Verifying the Hypothesis:\nGiven the Trace data and metric analysis, the hypothesis \"aiops-k8s-08 could be the root cause due to node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes reduction impacting services like redis-cart-0\" is supported.\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes reduction causing latency spikes in services hosted such as redis-cart-0, cartservice-2, and checkoutservice-1.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Node aiops-k8s-08 experienced a reduction in memory availability correlated with increased latency and errors in associated services.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Conclusion\nThe hypothesis that aiops-k8s-08 is experiencing memory issues leading to service degradation is consistent with both the metric data and the node-pod mapping. The performance impacts seen in services hosted on this node further affirm this deduction.", "trace_analysis_findings": "经过对调用链路异常数据的分析，我们发现以下关键证据与假设相关：\n\n### 关键调用链异常\n1. `aiops-k8s-08` 相关的异常组件：\n   - `checkoutservice-1` 调用自身产生显著延迟：\n     - `hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart`: 延迟约 3.18 倍\n     - `hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation`: 延迟约 3.10 倍\n     - `hipstershop.PaymentService/Charge`: 延迟约 2.73 倍\n   - `checkoutservice-1` 调用 `ShippingService/GetQuote`：延迟约 2.99 倍\n2. **错误类型分析**\n   - 异常集中在 `checkoutservice` 与相关组件（如 `shippingservice`、`cartservice`）的复杂交互路径。\n\n### 核心分析\n在几乎所有的调用链中，显著延迟都围绕 `aiops-k8s-08` 发生，特别是 `checkoutservice` 产生的多次显著延迟与自身节点上的其他服务存在交互。这与“aiops-k8s-08 的内存问题可能导致依赖服务延迟”假设高度吻合。\n\n### 初步结论\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"内存可用字节减少影响了 checkoutservice 的性能，而 checkoutservice 是多个下游服务异常的交错点。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常中 aiops-k8s-08 节点，checkoutservice 自身调用的延迟显著增加；多个调用延迟倍数 > 2.73 表明系统瓶颈集中于此。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
